      <title>苹果将​​在应用商店与 Spotify 的斗争中受到欧盟反垄断令的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/apple-set-to-be-hit-by-eu-antitrust-order-in-app-store-fight-with-spotify</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧盟对大型科技公司的最新打击中，苹果公司可能面临巨额罚款，并可能被禁止应用商店规则，据称该公司曾利用这些规则来挫败音乐流媒体竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/apple-set-to-be-hit-by-eu-antitrust-order-in-app-store-fight-with-spotify</guid>
